702864f-b.title: Brooklyn: 84th Street - 17th Avenue
702864f-b.text:
84th Street, south side, between Seventeenth and Sixteenth Aves.,
and showing a view of St, John's Lutheran Church and the Cemetery
of New Utrecht Dutch Reformed Church.
June 9, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, from another angle.
June 9, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
